  { name:"Slap Battles",            emoji:"👋", genre:"pvp",      vibe:"casual",      players:"60k+",  placeId:6403373529,      visits:"3B+",   rating:"94%", maxPlayers:"10", genre2:"PvP / Party",                 dev:"Tencelll",                   desc:"Slap people off the arena. Unlock 100+ gloves with wild abilities. Chaotic fun.", fullDesc:"Slap Battles is exactly what it sounds like — you slap players off a platform using gloves with wildly different abilities. Over 100 gloves to unlock ranging from simple to completely broken. Some have secret badges tied to them. Massive community, constant updates, and one of the highest-rated games on Roblox at 94%." },
